SUMMARY:Interchange Message: WEMBLEY PARK STATION: From Monday 10 March 
 until Autumn 2026\, no lift service between the street (Wembley Way / car 
 park) and ticket hall. Step-free access is still available by using the 
 entrance/exit on Bridge Road which is level between street and ticket 
 hall. Lifts remain available to all platforms.
